# - Find MyGUI includes and library
#
# This module defines
# MYGUI_INCLUDE_DIRS
# MYGUI_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use MYGUI.
# MYGUI_LIB_DIR, the location of the libraries
# MYGUI_FOUND, If false, do not try to use MYGUI
